Thank you for registering for the Creator Workflows Train Experience in Sydney. Please keep this email as it will serve as instructions for the experience.

 

Credentials:

username: Trigger➛Registration Record➛First Name.Trigger➛Registration Record➛Last Name

password (temp): ServiceNow2022 

 

Step 1: Login to the ServiceNow Walk-up experience and check-in for your Creator Workflows Train Experience.  https://stevemccluskeydemoq.service-now.com/now/servicenow-express/walk-up

Step 2. Pick your CreatorCon Location

Step 3: Click Check-in

Step 4: Visit the booth see the queue or check out the queue from your mobile device: https://stevemccluskeydemoq.service-now.com/now/servicenow-express/walk-up

 

***Alternative message***
